---
title: "Figure 9 — Multi-source full-text retrieval pipeline for DAS/Methods enrichment"
---
flowchart TD
    Start([DOI from citation entry]) --> Copernicus{Copernicus<br/>journal?<br/>10.5194}
    Copernicus -->|yes| CopGet[Direct article HTML<br/>open OA]
    Copernicus -->|no| Wiley{AGU/Wiley<br/>10.1029, 10.1002,<br/>10.1111}
    Wiley -->|yes| WileyTDM[Wiley TDM API<br/>token: WILEY_TDM_TOKEN<br/>returns PDF, parsed by pypdf]
    Wiley -->|no| Elsevier{Elsevier<br/>10.1016}
    Elsevier -->|yes| ElsevierTDM[Elsevier TDM API<br/>token: ELSEVIER_TDM_TOKEN<br/>returns XML]
    Elsevier -->|no| Unpaywall[Unpaywall API<br/>oa_locations, all hosts<br/>PDF first then HTML]
    CopGet --> Success
    WileyTDM --> Success
    ElsevierTDM --> Success
    Unpaywall -->|hit| Success
    Unpaywall -->|miss| OpenAlex[OpenAlex API<br/>institutional repositories<br/>Oxford ORA, Soton ePrints,<br/>Reading Centaur, NOAA]
    OpenAlex -->|hit| Success
    OpenAlex -->|miss| S2[Semantic Scholar API<br/>openAccessPdf field]
    S2 -->|hit| Success
    S2 -->|miss| DOIRedirect[DOI redirect<br/>last-resort]
    DOIRedirect -->|hit| Success
    DOIRedirect -->|miss| Failed([fetch_failed])
    Success([HTML or PDF text]) --> Extract[Extract DAS, Methods,<br/>and marker contexts]
    Extract --> LLM[Append to abstract<br/>send to Gemini classifier]
    LLM --> Decision{Engagement<br/>level changed?}
    Decision -->|yes| Flip[Apply flip<br/>record provenance]
    Decision -->|no| Keep[Keep label]

    style Start fill:#e3f2fd
    style Success fill:#c8e6c9
    style Failed fill:#ffcdd2
    style Flip fill:#fff9c4
